# Copy this file to taste/.env (which is gitignored) and paste your Slack token.
# One-time, lets /taste-pull download real image files into taste/images/.
#
# How to get the token (workspace admin, ~5 min):
# 1. Go to https://api.slack.com/apps → Create New App → From scratch → pick this workspace.
# 2. OAuth & Permissions → User Token Scopes → add: files:read
# 3. Install to Workspace, authorize.
# 4. Copy the "User OAuth Token" (starts with xoxp-) and paste it below.
SLACK_TOKEN=xoxp-your-token-here
